title: The List with Colleen Lopez 08.17.2017 - 09 PM
description:
The Fashion Edit is here! This week we're talking about Modern Boho featuring Lucky Brand, LaBellum by Hillary Scott, Lysse, and more. Curator and host Colleen Lopez takes the guesswork out of style by showcasing her weekly favorites.
